A **gold loan** allows you to pledge your gold ornaments or coins and get instant funds — typically 75–85% of the gold value. Gold loan interest rates range from 7% p.a. at banks to 28–29% at NBFCs. They are ideal for short-term emergencies due to quick disbursal (30 minutes) but can be expensive if held for long periods.
